text: Lavilleneuve-au-Roi is a commune in the Haute-Marne department in northeastern France. Between 1972 and 2012, it was part of the commune of Autreville-sur- la-Renne. == Related pages == * Communes of the Haute-Marne department ==References== Category:Communes in Haute-Marne
title: Lavilleneuve-au-Roi
